description: Fresh off a heartbreak, enigmatic starving artist Hunter and alluring, confident Ruby have a whirlwind romance in Venice Beach, but can it survive the harsh realities of her glitzy NYC art world?

title: Not Going Quietly
description: Ady Barkan's life is upended when he is diagnosed with ALS, but a confrontation with a powerful senator catapults him to national fame and ignites a once-in-a-generation political movement.

title: Texas True Crime
description: Everything is bigger in Texas, even the crime. The Lone Star state is home to some of the most brutal crimes in the country, and the most bizarre and outrageous. Texas True Crime takes you on a journey through firsthand bone-chilling accounts and never-before-seen photos and video from the investigations.

title: Sleeping With a Killer
description: It follows people who have tragic endings at the hands of husbands, wives, former friends, and lovers.

title: When Sharks Attack... and Why
description: From America's coastlines to exotic beaches around the world, shark attacks are becoming more unpredictable. Many of these attacks occur suddenly, in large numbers and in unexpected locations — puzzling locals and scientists alike. Experts investigate these mysterious incidents to discover what is affecting some of nature’s most feared fish.

title: Menorah in the Middle
description: Sarah is headed back to her hometown for Hanukkah with news of her engagement. Upon returning she finds out that her father had a heart attack and things have gotten out of hand.

title: Cinderella: The Reunion, A Special Edition of 20/20
description: 2022 marks the 25th anniversary of ABC airing Rodgers & Hammerstein’s “Cinderella” (1997), a revolutionary TV musical that embraced racial diversity in casting and has impacted generations over the years, starring an all-star cast led by Brandy Norwood as Cinderella and Whitney Houston as her fairy godmother. ABC News is producing a news special dedicated to the legacy of this film, reflecting how the idea of a princess has evolved and what makes the film still relevant today.

title: Keluarga Cemara: The Series
description: Euis and four of his friends, namely Deni, Rindu, Andi, and Ima, better known as Geng Kampung, are currently in high school and will take part in the national level quiz competition.

title: PSY Summer Swag 2022
description: Filmed in the summer of 2022, this concert will let fans relive the rapper's SUMMER SWAG concert in South Korea where fans jumped, danced, and sang along to his well-known melodies and beats while being showered with water sprays.

title: Irresistible
description: Kimhan and Mookarin were engaged to be married but a tragedy destroyed their happiness.  Mon, Kimhan's sister, was found dead and her husband Tada,  Mook's brother, was accused of killing her.

title: Santa Games
description: When beloved Santa Charles finally decides to retire from his career as a mall Santa, a series of interviews to replace him turns into an all-out competition.

title: Shark Attack Files
description: Scientific experts research about the bizarre and fascinating shark behavior based on real footage captured by professionals and bystanders.

title: CMA Fest: 50 Years of Fan Fair
description: Showcases the story of the largest and longest-running Country Music festival: the CMA Fest.

title: Huluween Dragstravaganza
description: Welcome to the hilarious Huluween drag variety show that’s serving you glitz, glamor, and ghouls, honey. Legendary queens Ginger Minj and Monét X Change are tasked with putting on the most spooky, over-the-top show… OR ELSE. Thankfully, a slew of drag royalty, including Jackie Beat, Jujubee, Lady Bunny, Landon Cider, Manila Luzon, Mario Diaz, Mo Heart, and Selene Luna, pop in to help them out. And an extra special musical guest drops by (hint: it’s Kesha!) to make sure Dragstravaganza is absolutely to die for. So grab your wigs, put on your heels, and strap in. It’s fierce. Frightening. And freaking hilarious.

title: The Last Warrior
description: It tells the tale of a young girl named Jade and a terracotta warrior named Magnus who must team up to fight the creatures that keep attacking their Qin dynasty underground city, and who eventually fall in love.

title: TMZ Investigates: Gilgo Beach Serial Murders: Missed Warning Signs
description: The investigation puts the spotlight on a former police chief who went to great lengths to derail the investigation, in no small part because he himself was hiring prostitutes and didn't want a spotlight put on him.

title: The Housewife & the Shah Shocker
description: Follows Jen Shah, a star of Bravo's "The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City," who was arrested and indicted for fraud and money laundering.

title: 50/50 Flip
description: In order to make maximum profits, husband and wife team, Krystal and Dedric Polite use their 50/50 Flip Strategy to renovate a home with less than $50K in under 50 days. These real estate investors have flipped the flipping business in Burlington, North Carolina as they transform homes in the area Krystal and her family grew up in and currently reside. To them it's about creating affordable housing for everyone and not allowing a big developer to come in and out-price their hometown. Family is everything and by investing back in the community they also want to create generational wealth that they can build and leave to their two young boys and their kids' kids.

title: Try Harder!
description: In a universe where cool kids are nerds, the orchestra is world class and being Asian American is the norm, seniors at Lowell High School compete for the top prize: admission to the college of their dreams.

title: A Unicorn for Christmas
description: A young girl discovers a real-life unicorn at a Christmas carnival and must protect it from a greedy fair owner.

title: Behind The Table: A View Reunion
description: The special takes viewers inside the hotel room at the Essex House hotel in New York City where current and original co-host Joy Behar, the show’s first moderator Meredith Vieira and original panellists Star Jones and Debbie Matenopoulos auditioned 25 years ago.

title: Croc That Ate Jaws
description: Discover what happens when two of the deadliest predators face each other.

title: Missing
description: "Missing" is a docuseries that uncovers the untold stories of people who vanished, bringing to light compelling cold cases that never received the attention they deserved.  "Missing" seeks to correct that while uncovering clues that bring us closer to the truth.

title: Christmas Wars
description: It’s the most wonderful time of the year? or is it? The holiday season is known to be joyous, but for some it brings out trouble. From Black Friday shopping madness, to full family brawls, CHRISTMAS WARS gives viewers the gift of seeing the human behavior that will secure a place on Santa's Naughty list.

title: Sarah's Mountain Escape
description: Sarah Richardson heads west to take on her biggest challenge yet, purchasing a dated and drab 5,000-square-foot Bavarian-inspired B&B in Whistler, BC. Audiences will step inside Sarah’s life with husband Alex and daughters Robin and Fiona as they travel across the country to transform the property into an efficient and profitable, four-season luxury vacation rental. It’s a massive undertaking as Sarah juggles the demands of managing a “back to the studs” renovation on the west coast while running her design business in Toronto and raising two kids.

title: Mountain Men Ultimate Marksman
description:
From TV promo on the History channel:

"Each week we bring four of the worlds best marksman to this ranch to compete with historical weapons using primitive knives, bows, and even century's old firearms. The worlds best marksmen shoot like mountain men."

title: American Rapstar
description: A new scene of troubled, lo-fi young rappers has emerged from Trump's America, utilizing the SoundCloud streaming platform to quickly become the most culturally disruptive force in hip hop, shocking the world with their rambunctious antics, prescription drug use, facial tattoos, and rebellious punk energy. We examine the SoundCloud rap scene's biggest stars from within the culture as well placing them in the broader musical context in an attempt to understand how we arrived here and where we are headed.

title: Farmhouse Facelift
description: Siblings Billy Pearson, a craftsman contractor, and Carolyn Wilbrink, a designer, tackle the toughest farmhouse renovations for their clients, bringing stunning designs and customized modern conveniences to each new project.

title: Swan Boy
description: An anthropomorphic 20-something swan of low station and (in his finest moments) medium intelligence gets into trouble ranging from the mundane to the fantastic to the surreal.

title: Starkeisha
description: A woman, stressed before an import job interview,  goes on a journey of self-discovery through her own subconscious.

title: Meekah
description: Meekah and her best friend Blippi have exciting and educational adventures together as they explore the wonders of science and nature.

title: Dirty Rotten Cleaners
description: Teams of extreme cleaners tackle jaw-dropping messes, mould, bacteria and biohazards as they dive into a never-before-seen side of the Sunshine State.

title: All I Want For Christmas
description: A beloved Black mall Santa wants to find the perfect replacement before he retires, while a teen is depending on him to help reunite her battling parents.

title: Cheese: A Love Story
description: An exploration and celebration of one of the world’s most beloved foods through the lens of Afrim Pristine, the world’s youngest Maître Fromager, or cheese master. In a six-part journey, Afrim travels to some of the most iconic places and secret hidden gems you’ve never heard of to show the world of cheese like it’s never been seen before.

title: Trading Up with Mandy Rennehan
description: Trading Up with Mandy Rennehan follows Blue Collar CEO(TM) and multi-million dollar designer and construction mogul Mandy Rennehan, as she cranks the residential resale reno business up a notch with three stellar property overhauls in her beloved hometown of Yarmouth, Nova Scotia. A proud and respectfully uncensored member of the trades since her teens, Mandy went from firing up power tools to landing a coveted spot amongst Canada's Top CEO's and most Powerful Women list. Now, Mandy's putting her money where her heart is and her latest residential real estate projects are not only investments, they're an opportunity to bring some very deserving apprentices along for the ride as she mentors them and prepares them for successful careers in the" business " of the trades. No ant infestation, collapsing foundation or water infiltration will stand in Mandy's way as she transforms these neglected historic properties into gorgeous desirable homes, inspiring and teaching everyone along the way. There are many bumps (and a few pot holes) in the road on this journey but heart and humour always prevail.

title: Project Bakeover
description: In Project Bakeover renowned pastry chef, master chocolatier and entrepreneur Steve Hodge throws a lifeline to struggling bakery businesses on the brink of losing it all. Drawing on his finely honed chef skills, his passion for desserts and his business acumen, Steve reinvigorates and inspires the desperate bakery owners, while design guru Tiffany Pratt transforms their tired, uninspired bakeries into warm and welcoming spaces. Together they get these businesses turned around and on the road to success.

title: Rachael Ray's Italian Dream Home
description: Follows Rachael Ray as she realizes her lifelong dream of owning and renovating a home in Tuscany.

title: Roman to the Rescue
description: Follows 10-year-old rescuer Roman McConn on his journey to find homes for adorable shelter dogs. Roman teams up with social media influencers to make next-level adoption videos that help dogs find their perfect forever families.

title: Wall of Bakers
description: Wall of Bakers challenges contestants to take on a different panel of tough judges drawn from the culinary world.

title: Deep Fried Dynasty
description: An inside look at how the imaginative fried foods of the State Fair of Texas come to life and the millions of dollars on the line for the family-run small businesses involved.

title: First-Time Buyer
description: Remember buying your first home? Easy peasy—or not so much? Now add the most competitive market ever into the mix and the pressure is unreal! Watch what happens when first-time buyers go all in, guided by the expertise of a REALTOR, in First-Time Buyer.

title: True Crime: The Search for the Versace Killer
description: Andrew Cunanan shocked Chicago and the nation with a high-profile murder spree that claimed five victims in four months in 1997, including fashion icon Gianni Versace. The nationwide manhunt captivated the country, searching for a killer on the run.

title: Gut Job
description: Pro athlete turned all-star builder Sebastian Clovis is on a mission to guide homeowners through the biggest renovations of their lives, bringing his creativity, support and team to each project.

title: Tiny Kitchen Cook-Off
description: Host Monica Padman interviews celebrity guests, while they attempt to re-create tiny recipes from the Tastemade Tiny Kitchen.

title: Peckham's Finest
description: The everyday life of a diverse and aspirational group of young people living in Peckham, an eclectic pocket of London.

title: Styled
description: This reality series, produced by Bunim-Murray Productions and the Margaret Maldonado Agency, follows the real lives (friendship, love, & career) of five junior assistants as they toil for three glamorous, high-end celebrity stylists. The documentary series follows the young junior assistants on the job -- music videos, movies, red carpets, etc -- and also follows them in their off-hours as they find romance, plot against each other, and try to make it big in a difficult industry, all while living on a meager junior assistant salary -- and all while looking great!

title: House of Ali
description: Step inside the electric world of luxury home designer Ali Budd as she pulls back the curtain to reveal the décor and drama behind the million-dollar renovations that have put her on the map, from single-room edits to whole-home builds.

title: Dois Tempos
description: A story of two girls who travel through time and change places from 1922 to 2022.

title: India Bites with Shrimoyee
description: India Bites is a docu-series created and presented by Chef Shrimoyee, which aims to break stereotypes about Indian culture through food and conversations. Come and explore a never seen before side to modern India.

title: House of Grucci
description: Follows Fifth-Generation President and CEO Phil Grucci of Fireworks by Grucci, Revealing Family History, Challenges and Triumphs as the Company Prepares for Major Performances.

title: Backroad Truckers
description: Welcome to the crazy world of "hot-shot truckers": a special breed of independent truckers who will haul anything, anywhere, at any time. This unscripted series follows two rival families and their crews as they tackle some of the most harrowing roads and dangerous off-road locations of northern British Columbia in their custom :monster" trucks. These bands of maniacs will do anything to get the job done: delivering and recovering urgent and vital cargo. And if they don't have right truck or tool for the job, they simply "git'er done", because for them, it's more than a day's work--it's a lifestyle.

title: Frankie vs the Internet
description: The internet's hottest culinary creators face off to turn social media's biggest viral food trends into real life dishes. They've got the likes and the views, but can they bring it in the heat of competition?

title: Merry Kiss Cam
description: When two people from very different worlds meet on a hockey kiss cam, could it lead to love?

title: Beyond the Headlines
description: The series focuses on a variety of situations of crime-torn families, abduction survival tales, poisonous love triangles, brainwashing cases, battles to safeguard vulnerable children, and parental crimes.

title: Rachael Ray's Rebuild
description: Hits close to home for Rachael whose life changed forever when her home and all her belongings were burned to the ground in a fire, inspiring her to rebuild her dream home and realize how important home is to her.
